                   "PETER'S QUEST: FOR THE LOVE OF DAPHNE"
                              - version 1.2 -

                                    by
                               David W. Meny
										 
Short Description:

   This is an arcade game for the Amiga where you, Peter, must traverse
through 20 levels to save your girlfriend Daphne who has been captured by
the evil Brutus.  Includes digitized sound and colorful graphics.  This
new version also includes options which can be bought to enhance gameplay,
such as super speed, super jump, rocket pack, and more!

Dated: November 20, 1991



